summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2761, for the improvement of lot one (1), block 38, Commercial Street Steam Motor Addition to the City of Seattle, and certain other property in the City of Seattle, by filling the same as a sanitary measure, under Ordinance No. 33029 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
